{"tid":1839614,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［能防TG的面罩，真不能防SARS ? ］","createTime":"2020-01-24T13:29:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T16:40:48.000Z","uid":23830,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"14a771f02baa23bec8d0cfc97ef6465b2f061477","tid":1839614,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:29:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">隔到微粒未必隔到細菌，所以手術醫護口罩合防沙示。<br />\n防毒豬咀對化學嘅，會用化學反應去中和，但對生物未必有用。<br />\n3m嘅濾芯有5/6種，真係要睇清楚先可以對症下藥。<br />\n唔敢講防毒豬咀一定唔得，但生物同化學真係兩樣嘢，一定要睇清楚說明。<br />\n戴錯無效用的=無戴。<br />\n印象中之前有人整理過濾芯嘅功能表，搵返來看比較好。<br />\n<br />\n*望有化學高手指點迷津，因似乎醫護口罩供應會有高危，全世界都需要。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HjggfcP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHjggfcP.jpg&h=dae6ddcb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f078bf691ffeea1bcacc9796fb2cd4b52614fa84","tid":1839614,"uid":308546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"睇03年啲紀錄片 沈祖堯都有戴過6200+P100的"},{"pid":"6227ab8036ca9143aa10950491c1dd86bc6bcc00","tid":1839614,"uid":162008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:34:15.000Z","msg":"有用知識推<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">要話俾醫護知，無論你地決定係點，市民會支持你地</span></span><br />\n<br />\n原Post<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">大家支唔支持醫護大罷工？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">入黎幫手推十次</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1837575\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1837575</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n</span>"},{"pid":"a2efab799c3130fc8024a82c4d246bfe96efd24a","tid":1839614,"uid":312333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:49:24.000Z","msg":"能，不過用一次就要換新"},{"pid":"3567c9f02947901a699238e8176e48b125668a1c","tid":1839614,"uid":23830,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-