oride (CK), Cyclohexane, Fluorine, Formaldehyde, Hydrogen Chloride, Hydrogen Cyanide (AC)<br />\nHydrogen Sulfide, Lewisite, Mustard (HD), Nerve Agent, Nitrogen Dioxide, Nuisance Dusts, Nuisance Odors, Oleoresin Capsicum (OC, Pepper Gas), Organic Vapors w/ Boiling Point &gt;65 Degree C, Particulates, Phosgene, Phosphine,Radioactive Particulates, Sarin (GB), Soman (GD) Sulfur Dioxide, Tabun (GA), Toluene, <span style=\"color: violet;\">Virus</span>, VX, Xylene.<br />\n<br />\nThe M61 filters have a predicted shelf-life of 5 years (when sealed and packaged)."},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:14:05.000Z","msg":"40mm 罐？<br />\n<br />\n而家講3M 豬嘴喎，答啲有關嘅得唔得？"},{"pid":"e1dd4bfae38819ead6d889d5ec38a08213b4f1f3","tid":1839614,"uid":392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:15:28.000Z","msg":"你個罐預左用一次就要掉"},{"pid":"c31ae15acb798eb9979e28cc2088106a13eba8d7","tid":1839614,"uid":29460,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"f078bf691ffeea1bcacc9796fb2cd4b52614fa84","tid":1839614,"uid":308546,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T13:32:32.000Z","msg":"睇03年啲紀錄片 沈祖堯都有戴過6200+P100的"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:17:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2gxGzff.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2gxGzff.png&h=14b85ffc&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n睇圖 唔洗討論"},{"pid":"3a20fb869b1ab19fad6d56d918cdfaacaaed6fcc","tid":1839614,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:17:27.000Z","msg":"你化學filter左就留係個罐到，病毒會滋生，你諗住幾耐換一次罐？"},{"pid":"09304593ff0d1083d288bbfc0c102547c38fa179","tid":1839614,"uid":66719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:19:09.000Z","msg":"加上你要額外清潔個本體，你能唔能夠保證你清潔本體個陣唔會感染？"},{"pid":"1a0918ff59244b8931e3dc27a7ac18f84a139a53","tid":1839614,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-25T13:21:10.000Z","msg":"Filter 用p100 2091"},{"pid":"add2394c2e105ef8584962